('scripture', 'text', 'mantra', 'Gayatri Mantra', '‡•ê ‡§≠‡•Ç‡§∞‡•ç‡§≠‡•Å‡§µ‡§É ‡§∏‡•ç‡§µ‡§É ‡§§‡§§‡•ç‡§∏‡§µ‡§ø‡§§‡•Å‡§∞‡•ç‡§µ‡§∞‡•á‡§£‡•ç‡§Ø‡§Ç ‡§≠‡§∞‡•ç‡§ó‡•ã ‡§¶‡•á‡§µ‡§∏‡•ç‡§Ø ‡§ß‡•Ä‡§Æ‡§π‡§ø ‡§ß‡§ø‡§Ø‡•ã ‡§Ø‡•ã ‡§®‡§É ‡§™‡•ç‡§∞‡§ö‡•ã‡§¶‡§Ø‡§æ‡§§‡•ç‡•§', 'The most sacred mantra in Hinduism, invoking the divine light to illuminate our understanding and guide us toward truth.', '["mantra", "gayatri", "sacred", "vedic", "meditation"]', 'sa', 'beginner', 'https://example.com/audio/gayatri-mantra.mp3', 'Om Bhur Bhuvah Svah Tat Savitur Varenyam Bhargo Devasya Dhimahi Dhiyo Yo Nah Prachodayat', 'Om Bhoor Bhu-vah Svah Tat Sa-vi-tur Va-ren-yam Bhar-go De-vas-ya Dhee-ma-hi Dhee-yo Yo Nah Pra-cho-da-yat'),

('scripture', 'text', 'mantra', 'Maha Mantra (Hare Krishna)', '‡§π‡§∞‡•á ‡§ï‡•É‡§∑‡•ç‡§£ ‡§π‡§∞‡•á ‡§ï‡•É‡§∑‡•ç‡§£ ‡§ï‡•É‡§∑‡•ç‡§£ ‡§ï‡•É‡§∑‡•ç‡§£ ‡§π‡§∞‡•á ‡§π‡§∞‡•á‡•§ ‡§π‡§∞‡•á ‡§∞‡§æ‡§Æ ‡§π‡§∞‡•á ‡§∞‡§æ‡§Æ ‡§∞‡§æ‡§Æ ‡§∞‡§æ‡§Æ ‡§π‡§∞‡•á ‡§π‡§∞‡•á‡•§', 'The great mantra for deliverance, chanted to invoke the divine names of Krishna and Rama for spiritual purification and consciousness elevation.', '["mantra", "krishna", "hare", "chanting", "bhakti"]', 'sa', 'beginner', 'https://example.com/audio/hare-krishna.mp3', 'Hare Krishna Hare Krishna Krishna Krishna Hare Hare Hare Rama Hare Rama Rama Rama Hare Hare', 'Ha-re Krish-na Ha-re Krish-na Krish-na Krish-na Ha-re Ha-re Ha-re Ra-ma Ha-re Ra-ma Ra-ma Ra-ma Ha-re Ha-re'),

('saint', 'text', 'teaching', 'Vivekananda on Self-Confidence', 'Arise, awake, and stop not until the goal is reached! You have the power within you to achieve anything. Believe in yourself and that power will manifest. The moment I have realized God sitting in the temple of every human body, the moment I stand in reverence before every human being and see God in him - that moment I am free from bondage.', 'Swami Vivekanandas inspiring message about inner strength, self-belief, and recognizing the divine in all beings.', '["self_confidence", "motivation", "spirituality", "inner_strength"]', 'en', 'beginner', null, null, null),

('scripture', 'text', 'prayer', 'Hanuman Chalisa (First Verse)', '‡§∂‡•ç‡§∞‡•Ä‡§ó‡•Å‡§∞‡•Å ‡§ö‡§∞‡§® ‡§∏‡§∞‡•ã‡§ú ‡§∞‡§ú ‡§®‡§ø‡§ú ‡§Æ‡§®‡•Å ‡§Æ‡•Å‡§ï‡•Å‡§∞‡•Å ‡§∏‡•Å‡§ß‡§æ‡§∞‡§ø‡•§ ‡§¨‡§∞‡§®‡§â‡§Ç ‡§∞‡§ò‡•Å‡§µ‡§∞ ‡§¨‡§ø‡§Æ‡§≤ ‡§ú‡§∏‡•Å ‡§ú‡•ã ‡§¶‡§æ‡§Ø‡§ï‡•Å ‡§´‡§≤ ‡§ö‡§æ‡§∞‡§ø‡•§‡•§', 'Opening verse of Hanuman Chalisa, seeking blessings from the Guru and preparing to sing the pure glories of Lord Rama.', '["hanuman", "prayer", "protection", "devotion", "rama"]', 'hi', 'intermediate', 'https://example.com/audio/hanuman-chalisa.mp3', 'Shri Guru Charan Saroj Raj Nij Man Mukur Sudhari Barnau Raghuvar Bimal Jasu Jo Dayak Phal Chari', null),

('scripture', 'text', 'mantra', 'Om Namah Shivaya', '‡•ê ‡§®‡§Æ‡§É ‡§∂‡§ø‡§µ‡§æ‡§Ø', 'The five-syllable mantra dedicated to Lord Shiva, meaning "I bow to Shiva" - representing the consciousness within all beings.', '["mantra", "shiva", "meditation", "consciousness", "sacred"]', 'sa', 'beginner', 'https://example.com/audio/om-namah-shivaya.mp3', 'Om Namah Shivaya', 'Om Na-mah Shi-va-ya'),

('scripture', 'text', 'mantra', 'Mool Mantra (Sikh)', '‡®á‡®ï ‡®ì‡®Ö‡©∞‡®ï‡®æ‡®∞ ‡®∏‡®§‡®ø ‡®®‡®æ‡®Æ‡©Å ‡®ï‡®∞‡®§‡®æ ‡®™‡©Å‡®∞‡®ñ‡©Å ‡®®‡®ø‡®∞‡®≠‡®â ‡®®‡®ø‡®∞‡®µ‡©à‡®∞‡©Å ‡®Ö‡®ï‡®æ‡®≤ ‡®Æ‡©Ç‡®∞‡®§‡®ø ‡®Ö‡®ú‡©Ç‡®®‡©Ä ‡®∏‡©à‡®≠‡©∞ ‡®ó‡©Å‡®∞ ‡®™‡©ç‡®∞‡®∏‡®æ‡®¶‡®ø ‡••', 'The fundamental teaching of Sikhism encapsulating the nature of God as described by Guru Nanak - One Creator, Truth, Fearless, Without hatred, Timeless form.', '["sikh", "mool_mantra", "oneness", "truth", "guru_nanak"]', 'pa', 'intermediate', null, 'Ik Onkar Sat Nam Karta Purakh Nirbhau Nirvair Akal Murat Ajuni Saibhan Gur Prasad', null);

